[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "被害状況、中破、作戦行動に一時的な制限あり",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_036_01122",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "はぁ、はぁ……やっぱり、みんな、強い……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_036_01123",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ベスティラ王妃",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "な、なんなのこいつら……王様より強いかも？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_708_036_01124",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "ベスティラ王妃、詳しいお話はブラオールの\n監察本部でうかがいます",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01125",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ベスティラ王妃",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "て、丁重に扱ってよ！\n私は王妃なんだから！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_708_036_01126",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "安心しろ。我々監察官は、誰でも分け隔てなく、\n同じ扱いをする",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01127",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "ふぅ……これでこちらの用件は解決できそうだ。\nあとのことは我々に任せろ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01128",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ええ、分かったわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01129",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "さて、と。次はこっちね。\n思った以上に過激に首を突っ込んできて驚いたけど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01130",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ヘルトたちに通常通りのパルメの役割を\nこなせって言われてたわよね。それがこれってこと？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01131",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "肯定。レスナたちの監視、そして危険分子の「管理」",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_036_01132",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "それを真面目にやっている。さすがヤドヴィガだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_01133",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "でもさ、キューンは見るからに\n乗り気じゃなかったよね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01134",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "そ、それは……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_036_01135",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "もうさ、無理しないでこっちに来なさいよ。\nヘルト怖いでしょ？　私が守ってあげるから、ね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01136",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "アタシもいるよ。シトリンは……まあ、分からないが",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_01137",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "でも、それはマスターに刃向かうことになるし……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_036_01138",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "肯定。我らが主の命令が最優先事項",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_036_01139",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "あー、もう！　シトリン！\nちょっとヤドヴィガの口と目を塞いで！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01140",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "ほいほい、面白そうだしここは手伝っちゃうよ。\nヤドヴィガ、ちょーっと黙っててね～",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_01141",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "む～、む～……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_036_01142",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "キューン、この際アウグストへの恩とか\nヤドヴィガのしがらみは置いといて……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01143",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ぶっちゃけ、どうなの？\n本心から、私たちと一緒には行けない？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01144",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "それは……そんなことは……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_036_01145",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "私……そっちに行きたい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_036_01146",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "言えたじゃないの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01147",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "マスターの言うことは分かるけど、冷たいなって思うし\nヘルト兄貴とゼロ姉貴は純粋に、怖い……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_036_01148",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "よーし、じゃあ超決まり！\nもうこのまま話し合ってもウダウダ平行線だし……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01149",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "あなたのこと、ヴァレリアお姉ちゃんが攫ってあげる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01150",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "うっ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_036_01151",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "っ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_036_01152",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "な、なんて力技な……\nここらへん、ヘルトの妹感あるなぁ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_01153",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "ま、でも昔からあんな感じで超越してたよ。\nナナの頃からさ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_01154",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "っていうか、誘拐なんてさ、やってること\nここの王妃様と変わんないじゃん",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_01155",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "私はあくまで身内だし！　それにこのほうが\n私たちに無理矢理連れ去られたって言い訳できるでしょ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01156",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "家族の間でも、同意なき連れ去りは\n法に触れるんだが……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01157",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ごめんエルス、見逃して……この二人は責任持って\n私が全力で守るから！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01158",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "ボス、親の虐待から子どもを守るのは\n一時避難に該当すると思いますよ～",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01159",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "む……しっかり勉強しているようだな。\nお前ももう、一人前かもしれないな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01160",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "本当ですか？　やったあ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01161",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 40,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "そもそもこいつらはなんなんだ。後ほど、\n事情を説明してもらうぞ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01162",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 41,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "……ヴァレリア、\nそこまで覚悟があるんなら、やってみな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_01163",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 42,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ええ……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01164",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]